title: Number of divorces in Sweden 2008 to 2018
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of divorces, containing a total of 11 data points.
Overall Number of divorces has increased over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2012 and 2013.
Maximum Number of divorces, about 26933.0 was reported at Year 2013
Minimum Number of divorces about 22580.0 was reached at Year 2008
